text: Ishkinovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Uralsky Selsoviet,Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 186 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 42 km from Uchaly, 6 km from Uralsk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Ishkinovo
